<p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">"&ldquo;Such activities include </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">(but are not limited to)</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> snuggling, holding hands, going on romantic dates, exchanging romantic words, sharing a bed, </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">[and]</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> being in a committed relationship</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">,&rdquo; she says</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">She explains these activities will feel different from how they would with </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">someone you want </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">platonic</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> intimacy with."</span></p>
