<p style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: 'Courier New'; color: #000000; background-color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">"&ldquo;The only time a sex dream may give you some inclination about your sexual orientation is if before you had the dream you were already questioning your sexuality,&rdquo; she says."</span></p>
